1 Totara Tasty Cheddar
1 Croissants
1 Garlic Aioli
1 Shaved Champagne Ham
2 Decadent Chocolate Pot

• Preheat oven to 220°C/200°C fan-forced.
• Thinly slice Totara Cheddar cheese.
• Cut croissants in half horizontally.

• Spread croissant bases with garlic aioli and top with cheese and shaved
Champagne ham. Top with croissant tops and place on an oven tray.

• Bake until cheese is melted, 5-8 mins.